msgid " Universal Omnitech Cyberleg (Alpha)"
msgstr "环球全能科技人造腿（阿尔法）"

msgid ""
"2 attacks with less chance for a critical. May hit adjacent characters. Uses"
" 6 bullets."
msgstr "暴击几率较低的2次攻击。可以击中邻近角色。使用6发子弹。"

msgid ""
"2 attacks with less chance for critical DMG. May hit adjacent characters. "
"Uses 8 bullets."
msgstr "暴击几率较低的2次攻击。可以击中邻近角色。使用8发子弹。"

msgid ""
"5 attacks in one round that do half or normal damage. -15% to hit. Uses 10 "
"bullets."
msgstr "一个回合内5次攻击，造成正常伤害或其一半的伤害。-15%命中率。使用10发子弹。"

msgid "A MilSpec SMG that's easily found in streets."
msgstr "很容易在街头找到的军标冲锋枪。"

msgid "A MilSpec SMG that's easily found in streets. Includes silencer."
msgstr "很容易在街头找到的军标冲锋枪。带消声器。"

msgid "A basic assault rifle that is surprisingly good."
msgstr "惊人地好使的一把基础突击步枪。"

msgid ""
"A basic combat drone that every rigger should own at least once in their "
"shadow career."
msgstr "这种基础战斗无人机值得每一个机械师在他的暗影生涯中拥有过至少一次。"

msgid "A bite from the powerful jaws of a hellbeast."
msgstr "地狱野兽用强健下颌进行撕咬。"

msgid "A blast of lightning that also does ongoing -10 HP. Lasts 2 RNDS."
msgstr "一次闪电冲击，还造成持续的-10生命值。持续2回合。"

msgid "A blast of wind."
msgstr "一阵风力冲击。"

msgid "A bolt of lightning that targets a single enemy and also does -1 AP."
msgstr "瞄准单个敌人的闪电箭，还可造成-1行动点。"

msgid ""
"A breath of fire that does -8 HP DMG and does -4 HP DMG that last for 2 "
"RNDS."
msgstr "火焰吐息造成-8生命值伤害，并且持续2回合-4生命值伤害。"

msgid ""
"A calm approach and a swarm of drones should get the job done. For a price."
msgstr "一群无人机静静地逼近就能完成任务。要有个价码。"

msgid "A claw attack that does -10 HP of DMG and then -1 AP for 3 RNDS."
msgstr "造成-10生命值伤害的爪击，并造成持续3回合-1行动点。"

msgid "A crushing claw attack that does -8 HP DMG."
msgstr "造成-8生命值伤害的粉碎性爪击"

msgid ""
"A deck and confidence is all a good decker needs. And nuyen. Always need "
"more of that."
msgstr "控制板和自信是一名优秀黑客的全部所需。还有钱。钱多多益善。"

msgid ""
"A decker doesn’t escape reality in the Matrix, a decker makes it. Quality is"
" variable."
msgstr "黑客不会在矩阵中逃避现实，黑客是在制造现实。质量有好有坏。"

msgid "A explosion of acid that also delivers ongoing -5 HP. Lasts 2 RNDS."
msgstr "一次酸液爆炸，还可以带来持续-5生命值。持续2回合。"

msgid "A fiery explosion that also does ongoing -10 HP for 1 RNDS."
msgstr "一次火焰爆炸，还可以带来持续-10生命值。持续1回合。"

msgid "A fiery explosion that also does ongoing -10 HP for 2 RNDS."
msgstr "一次火焰爆炸，还可以带来持续-10生命值。持续2回合。"

msgid ""
"A fighter fights. A samurai does the job that needs doing and does it with "
"honor."
msgstr "武士就要战斗，就要满怀荣耀做该做的事。"

msgid "A fist of Rock"
msgstr "岩石拳头"

msgid "A giant bite from the maw of the abomination."
msgstr "憎恶喉管的强劲撕咬。"

msgid ""
"A good brawl is a lot like a mosh pit – only with less blood and death."
msgstr "打一场漂亮架就像在摇滚现场疯狂一样，只不过没那么多血腥和死亡。"

msgid ""
"A good run needs novahot drones, wiz firepower, tactical smarts, and nuyen "
"upfront."
msgstr "要完成任务需要厉害的无人机，强大的火力，高明的策略和预付的报酬。"

msgid "A heavy axe made for cutting up your enemies."
msgstr "用来砍翻敌人的重斧。"

msgid ""
"A heavy pistol created to perform perfectly under the most extreme "
"situations."
msgstr "在最极端的环境下仍能表现完美的重手枪。"

msgid ""
"A heavy pistol with silencer created to perform under the most extreme "
"situations."
msgstr "在最极端的环境下仍能表现完美的带消声器的重手枪。"

msgid "A heavy war sword that can cut a metahuman in half."
msgstr "可以将超人类劈成两半的重型战刀。"

msgid ""
"A hunk of metal that can be used to crush skulls. May do AP DMG on a "
"critical hit."
msgstr "可以砸碎颅骨的大块金属。暴击时可造成行动点伤害。"

msgid "A line of fire controlled by the caster and directed at one target."
msgstr "一道由施法着控制、喷向一个目标的火线。"

msgid "A low grade pistol carried mostly by guards."
msgstr "多由守卫佩戴的低端手枪。"

msgid "A low grade pistol carried mostly by guards. Includes Silencer."
msgstr "多由守卫佩戴的低端手枪。带消声器。"

msgid "A low-end all purpose shotgun."
msgstr "低端的通用型霰弹枪。"

msgid "A magical explosion that ignores normal armor and targets Willpower."
msgstr "无视普通护甲和目标意志的魔法爆炸。"

msgid "A makeshift, home-made shotgun."
msgstr "凑合使用的自制霰弹枪。"

msgid ""
"A medkit on wheels, it's a runner's best friend in the heat of a firefight."
msgstr "带轮子的医疗箱，是狂奔者在白热化战斗中的良友。"

msgid "A modern revolver that gives increased damage but less combat options."
msgstr "威力增强但缺乏战斗变数的现代左轮枪。"

msgid ""
"A mouth of teeth that rips your flesh and does a minimum of 11 HP and 1 AP "
"damage."
msgstr "尖牙利齿撕裂你的血肉，造成最少11点生命值伤害和1点行动点伤害。"

msgid ""
"A mouth of teeth that rips your flesh and does a minimum of 15 HP and 1 AP "
"damage."
msgstr "尖牙利齿撕裂你的血肉，造成最少15点生命值伤害和1点行动点伤害。"

msgid ""
"A mouth of teeth that rips your flesh and does a minumum of 7 HP damage."
msgstr "尖牙利齿撕裂你的血肉，造成最少7点生命值伤害。"

msgid ""
"A mouth of teeth that rips your flesh and does a minumum of 8 HP damage."
msgstr "尖牙利齿撕裂你的血肉，造成最少8点生命值伤害。"

msgid "A old Lone Star hoverdrone that has been given a weapon upgrade."
msgstr "一架经过升级的老旧孤星无人机。"

msgid "A poison fist that does DMG and then causes -6 HP for 1 RND."
msgstr "一次造成伤害的毒性拳击，然后造成1回合-6生命值。"

msgid "A powerful attack program directed at one target for 100 IP DMG."
msgstr "指向一个目标的强力攻击程序，造成100结合度伤害。"

msgid "A powerful attack program directed at one target for 150 IP DMG."
msgstr "指向一个目标的强力攻击程序，造成150结合度伤害。"

msgid "A powerful attack program directed at one target for 175 IP DMG."
msgstr "指向一个目标的强力攻击程序，造成175结合度伤害。"

msgid "A powerful attack program directed at one target, doing -100 IP DMG."
msgstr "指向一个目标的强力攻击程序，造成-100结合度伤害。"

msgid "A powerful attack program directed at one target, doing -125 IP DMG."
msgstr "指向一个目标的强力攻击程序，造成-125结合度伤害。"

msgid "A powerful attack program directed at one target, doing -75 IP DMG."
msgstr "指向一个目标的强力攻击程序，造成-75结合度伤害。"

msgid "A powerful attack program directed at one target."
msgstr "指向一个目标的强力攻击程序。"

msgid "A powerful blast of wind."
msgstr "一阵强风冲击。"

msgid "A powerful club attack"
msgstr "强力的棍击"

msgid "A powerful heavy pistol."
msgstr "威力强大的重型手枪。"

msgid "A powerful heavy pistol. Includes silencer."
msgstr "威力强大的重手枪。带消声器。"

msgid "A powerful magical 'punch' that ignores armor."
msgstr "无视护甲的强力魔法拳击。"

msgid ""
"A powerful magical bolt that ignores normal armor and targets Willpower."
msgstr "无视普通护甲和目标意志的强力魔法箭。"

msgid "A powerful shot of water."
msgstr "用水强力射击。"

msgid ""
"A powerful spit of bug venom that does base 20 HP and also reduces the Body "
"of a target by 2 for 3 rounds."
msgstr "一次强力喷吐，喷出的毒虫造成20点基础伤害并减少目标体质2点，持续3回合。"

msgid "A powerful talon swipe"
msgstr "强力的利爪扫击"

msgid "A punch from the fist of a ghoul that does base damage."
msgstr "尸鬼出拳造成基础伤害。"

msgid ""
"A requirement for Riggers and Deckers and those that want to use a smartlink"
" weapon."
msgstr "机械师、黑客和那些想要使用智能连接武器的人必备。"

msgid ""
"A shaman who doesn’t love conjuring isn't worth the spirits she can summon."
msgstr "不热爱召唤的萨满配不上她所能召唤的灵魂。"

msgid "A shot of water."
msgstr "用水射击。"

msgid "A shotgun seemingly made for Shadowrunners."
msgstr "似乎就是为暗影狂奔者打造的霰弹枪。"

msgid "A small sub-machine gun with big damage potential."
msgstr "潜藏巨大伤害的小型冲锋枪。"

msgid "A small sub-machine gun with big damage potential. Includes silencer."
msgstr "潜藏巨大伤害的小型冲锋枪。带消声器。"

msgid "A specialist's assault rifle used by corpsec units world wide."
msgstr "全球的集团安保所使用的专家突击步枪。"

msgid ""
"A specialist's assault rifle used by corpsec units. Slightly more accurate "
"than its competitors."
msgstr "集团安保所使用的专家突击步枪。比它的竞品稍微精准一些。"

msgid "A standard drone repair kit that repairs a minimum of 10 HP."
msgstr "至少修复10点生命值的标准无人机修复工具。"

msgid "A standard issue rifle."
msgstr "标准配备的步枪。"

msgid "A stolen ID card"
msgstr "偷来的身份卡"

msgid "A stream of acid that also does ongoing -6 HP for 1 RND."
msgstr "喷射酸液，还可使目标在1回合内受到-6生命值的持续伤害。"

msgid "A stream of acid that also does ongoing -6 HP for 2 RNDS."
msgstr "喷射酸液，还可使目标在2回合内受到-6生命值的持续伤害。"

msgid ""
"A strong body and mind command the powers of heaven. Not enough of one and "
"you burn."
msgstr "强健的身躯和意志可以操控天堂的力量。少一样都会灭亡。"

msgid "A stun spell which does -1 AP to the target."
msgstr "对目标造成-1行动点的眩晕法师。"

msgid ""
"A support drone that is equipped to lay a smoke trail anywhere you need it "
"most."
msgstr "辅助型无人机，在你需要的地方留下一道烟雾轨迹。"

msgid "A top-line shotgun for those that like the big damage."
msgstr "对喜欢高伤害的人来说是把极品霰弹枪。"

msgid "A work of art and a deadly weapon. May do AP DMG on a critical hit."
msgstr "一件一艺术品，一把致命武器。暴击时可造成行动点伤害。"

msgid "AJ"
msgstr "AJ"

msgid "AK-97"
msgstr "AK-97"

msgid "AK-97 (Smartlink)"
msgstr "AK-97（智能连接）"

msgid "AOE AP attack"
msgstr "区域性行动点攻击"

msgid "AOE Magic Attack"
msgstr "区域性魔法攻击"

msgid "AOE sleep attack"
msgstr "区域性沉睡攻击"

msgid "Accident"
msgstr "故障"

msgid "Accident: All Actions AP Cost +1"
msgstr "故障：所有行动消耗+1"

msgid "Acid Burst"
msgstr "酸性爆发"

msgid "Acid Stream 1"
msgstr "酸性喷射 1"

msgid "Acid Stream 2"
msgstr "酸性喷射 2"

msgid "Acid: HP -5 per RND"
msgstr "酸性：每回合生命值-5"

msgid "Acid: HP -6 per RND"
msgstr "酸性：每回合生命值-6"

msgid "Acid: HP -8 per RND"
msgstr "酸性：每回合生命值-8"

msgid ""
"Act. Do not react. Bend like the willow. Block like water. Move with a "
"purpose."
msgstr "身随心动，摆布不受，动似柳，静似水，成竹自在胸。"

msgid "Activate Mystic Armor"
msgstr "启用玄真护甲"

msgid "Activate Pain Resistance"
msgstr "启用痛苦抗性"

msgid "Activate Stride"
msgstr "启用大步流星"

msgid "Activate Wired Reflexes"
msgstr "启用跳线反射"

msgid "Activate counterstrike."
msgstr "启用反戈一击。"

msgid "Adding mana cover"
msgstr "增加魔法防护"

msgid "Adds Armor"
msgstr "增加护甲"

msgid "Adept"
msgstr "魔斗士"

msgid "Adept ninja outfit that grants the wearer Dodge +1"
msgstr "魔斗士忍者装束赋予穿着者躲闪+1"

msgid "Adept ninja outfit."
msgstr "魔斗士忍者装束"

msgid "Advanced Drone Repair Kit"
msgstr "高级无人机修复工具"

msgid "Advanced Medkit"
msgstr "高级医疗箱"

msgid "Agent Provocateur"
msgstr "秘密煽动者"

msgid "Aim 1"
msgstr "瞄准 1"

msgid "Aim 2"
msgstr "瞄准 2"

msgid "Aim 3"
msgstr "瞄准 3"

msgid "Aim: Accuracy +12%"
msgstr "瞄准：命中率+12%"

msgid "Aim: Accuracy +15%"
msgstr "瞄准：命中率+15%"

msgid "Aim: Accuracy +18%"
msgstr "瞄准：命中率+18%"

msgid "Aimed Burst"
msgstr "瞄准连射"

msgid "Aimed Shot"
msgstr "瞄准射击"

msgid "Air Barrier 1"
msgstr "空气屏障 1"

msgid "Air Barrier 2"
msgstr "空气屏障 2"

msgid "Air Barrier 3"
msgstr "空气屏障 3"

msgid "Alexander Falk"
msgstr "亚历山大·弗克"

msgid "Alexey"
msgstr "阿历克西"

msgid ""
"All enemies within a range of 3 squares of the spirit are infected for -5 "
"HP."
msgstr "灵魂3格范围内的所有敌人被感染，-5生命值。"

msgid ""
"All it takes is a rigger with the right equipment and lots of Johnson’s "
"cred."
msgstr "所需要的只是一个拥有合适装备的机械师以及很多的钱。"

msgid "Alley Mage Outfit"
msgstr "巷道魔法师装束"

msgid "Alley Punk"
msgstr "巷道朋克"

msgid "Alnur's Outfit"
msgstr "奥努尔的装束"

msgid ""
"Alpha level cyberlegs made by Universal Omnitech. Adds +8 HP, + 1 Quickness,"
" & + 1 Dodge"
msgstr "环球全能科技制造的阿尔法级人造腿。增加+8生命值，+1敏捷和+1躲闪"

msgid "An Ares Classic."
msgstr "经典战神武器。"

msgid "An advanced drone repair kit that repairs a minimum of 20 HP."
msgstr "至少修复20点生命值的高级无人机修复工具。"

msgid ""
"An area effect spell that increases the cost of magic by 1 AP. Lasts for 3 "
"RNDS."
msgstr "区域性法术，在其中使用法术增加1点行动点消耗。持续3回合。"

msgid ""
"An area effect spell that reduces any sound made in it to 0. Lasts for 4 "
"RNDS."
msgstr "使范围内的声响减到0的持续性法术。持续4回合。"

msgid ""
"An area effect spell that reduces the chance to target someone by 15%. Lasts"
" for 3 RNDS."
msgstr "使范围内瞄准目标的几率降低15%。持续3回合。"

msgid "An area-effect matrix attack that deals -100 IP DMG to IC and deckers."
msgstr "区域性矩阵攻击，对反入侵机制和黑客造成-100结合度伤害。"

msgid ""
"An area-effect matrix attack that deals -25 IP DMG to IC and deckers, and "
"roots them in place for 1 RND."
msgstr "区域性矩阵攻击，对反入侵机制和黑客造成-25结合度伤害，并将他们定在原处1回合。"

msgid ""
"An area-effect matrix attack that deals -50 IP DMG to IC and deckers, and "
"roots them in place for 1 RND."
msgstr "区域性矩阵攻击，对反入侵机制和黑客造成-50结合度伤害，并将他们定在原处1回合。"

msgid "An area-effect matrix attack that deals -50 IP DMG to IC and deckers."
msgstr "区域性矩阵攻击，对反入侵机制和黑客造成-50结合度伤害。"

msgid ""
"An area-effect matrix attack that deals -75 IP DMG to IC and deckers, and "
"roots them in place for 1 RND."
msgstr "区域性矩阵攻击，对反入侵机制和黑客造成-75结合度伤害，并将他们定在原处1回合。"

msgid "An area-effect matrix attack that deals -75 IP DMG to IC and deckers."
msgstr "区域性矩阵攻击，对反入侵机制和黑客造成-75结合度伤害。"

msgid ""
"An area-effect matrix attack that deals damage to IC and deckers, and roots "
"them in place for 1 round."
msgstr "区域性矩阵攻击，对反入侵机制和黑客造成伤害，并将他们定在原处1回合。"

msgid "An area-effect matrix attack that deals damage to IC and deckers."
msgstr "区域性矩阵攻击，对反入侵机制和黑客造成伤害。"

msgid "An arrow of fire that does 7-11 HP of damage."
msgstr "一支造成7-11点生命值伤害的火焰箭矢。"

msgid "An arrow of fire."
msgstr "带火的箭。"

msgid "An assault shotgun that has a burst fire option."
msgstr "具有连射模式的突击霰弹枪。"

msgid "An attack program that hits a decker's meat body for -15 HP."
msgstr "对黑客的肉体造成-15生命值伤害的攻击程序。"

msgid ""
"An easy favorite of Runners, combines high stopping power with ammo "
"capacity."
msgstr "狂奔者们的最爱，杀伤力高，弹容量足。"

msgid ""
"An effecive shock grenade. It does -2 AP to everyone caught in its blast."
msgstr "一种有效的震荡手雷。使爆炸范围内所有人-2行动点。"

msgid "An effecive shock grenade. It does -2 AP to everyone hit by its blast."
msgstr "一种有效的震荡手雷。使所有被爆炸击中的人-2行动点。"

msgid "An expert drone repair kit that repairs a minimum of 30 HP."
msgstr "至少修复30点生命值的专家无人机修复工具。"

msgid ""
"An old school revolver that gives increased damage but less combat options."
msgstr "威力增强但缺乏战斗变数的老式左轮枪。"

msgid "An unarmed melee attack that adds +1 to DMG."
msgstr "造成+1伤害的徒手近战攻击。"

msgid "An unarmed melee attack that can hit adjacent targets."
msgstr "可以击中邻近目标的徒手近战攻击。"

msgid "An unarmed melee attack that does more AP damage than HP damage."
msgstr "造成比生命值伤害更多的行动点伤害的徒手近战攻击。"

msgid "An unarmed melee attack that does more HP damage than AP damage."
msgstr "造成比行动点伤害更多的生命值伤害的徒手近战攻击。"

msgid "Andre Guillermo Aguirre's Outfit"
msgstr "安德烈·吉尔莫·阿基尔的装束"

msgid ""
"Arcane powers aren’t toys but they are fun to play with. Like a cat with a "
"mouse."
msgstr "秘法力量并非玩具，但却值得把玩。就像猫捉老鼠一样。"

msgid "Ares Alpha"
msgstr "战神阿尔法"

msgid "Ares Alpha (Smartlink)"
msgstr "战神阿尔法（智能连接）"

msgid "Ares Concussion Grenade"
msgstr "战神震荡手雷"

msgid "Ares Dermal Plating (Alpha)"
msgstr "战神皮肤膜（阿尔法）"

msgid "Ares Dermal Plating (Basic)"
msgstr "战神皮肤膜（基础）"

msgid "Ares High Explosive Grenade"
msgstr "战神高爆手雷"

msgid "Ares Predator"
msgstr "战神捕猎者"

msgid "Ares Predator (Silencer)"
msgstr "战神捕猎者（消声器）"

msgid "Ares Predator (Smartlink)"
msgstr "战神捕猎者（智能连接）"

msgid "Ares made stealth suit that grants Dodge +1, Movement +1"
msgstr "战神制造的潜行衣，使躲闪+1，行动力+1"

msgid "Ares made stealth suit."
msgstr "战神制造的潜行衣。"

msgid "Ares top of the line assault rifle."
msgstr "战神系列的顶级突击步枪。"

msgid "Ares' basic dermal armor plating implants. Adds +2 Armor"
msgstr "战神基础皮肤护甲植入体。增加+2护甲"

msgid ""
"Ares' top of the line concussion grenade does -3 AP to everyone in the blast"
" area."
msgstr "战神系列的顶级震荡手雷，使爆炸区域的所有人-3行动点。"

msgid ""
